    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-80af-8525-c2a4b3f5dcd0",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Teamwork is becoming an increasingly relevant skill to develop in the modern world. In an educational setting, not only do teams often lack support, but often fall short of forming optimal groups. The authors propose a new algorithm to form groups that uses uses a mix of AI and ontology:",
